<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Meu Perfil no GitHub</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #0d1117;
            color: #c9d1d9;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #161b22;
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #58a6ff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        p {
            color: #8b949e;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #238636;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #2ea043;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Olá, Mundo! 👋</h1>
        <p>Este é o meu site hospedado diretamente pelo GitHub. Aqui você vai encontrar meus projetos, códigos e um pouco sobre mim.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" class="btn">Ver meu GitHub</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
